        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libgimp/gimpdrawablefilter_pdb.c"
             line="577">Get a list of all available GEGL operation names for drawable
filters.

This procedure returns a list of all GEGL operation names available
for use with drawable filters.</doc>
