      <function name="operation_get_details"
                c:identifier="gimp_drawable_filter_operation_get_details"
                version="3.2">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libgimp/gimpdrawablefilter_pdb.c"
             line="615">Get information about a GEGL operation.

This procedure returns information about a GEGL operation. The
content of the list of information can vary across versions and
currently can contain:
- a human-readable title of the operation, - a description of the
operation's behaviour, - the categories the operation belongs to,
and - the license of the operation.
An operation can belong to no categories or to multiple categories.
Multiple categories are separated by the ':' character.
Some operation's license is not specifically set. In such cases, the
returned license is 'unknown'.</doc>
        <source-position filename="libgimp/gimpdrawablefilter_pdb.h"
                         line="63"/>
        <return-value transfer-ownership="none">
          <doc xml:space="preserve"
               filename="libgimp/gimpdrawablefilter_pdb.c"
               line="634">TRUE on success.</doc>
          <type name="gboolean" c:type="gboolean"/>
        </return-value>
        <parameters>
          <parameter name="operation_name" transfer-ownership="none">
            <doc xml:space="preserve"
                 filename="libgimp/gimpdrawablefilter_pdb.c"
                 line="617">The GEGL operation's name.</doc>
            <type name="utf8" c:type="const gchar*"/>
          </parameter>
          <parameter name="propnames"
                     direction="out"
                     caller-allocates="0"
                     transfer-ownership="full">
            <doc xml:space="preserve"
                 filename="libgimp/gimpdrawablefilter_pdb.c"
                 line="618">The names of properties.</doc>
            <array c:type="gchar***">
              <type name="utf8" c:type="gchar**"/>
            </array>
          </parameter>
          <parameter name="propvalues"
                     direction="out"
                     caller-allocates="0"
                     transfer-ownership="full">
            <doc xml:space="preserve"
                 filename="libgimp/gimpdrawablefilter_pdb.c"
                 line="619">The values of properties in the same order.</doc>
            <type name="ValueArray" c:type="GimpValueArray**"/>
          </parameter>
        </parameters>
      </function>
